=== 对话伙伴 ===
[[File:Hamid_Karzai_at_SCO_Summit.jpg|thumb]]在2004年的上合组织峰会上。]]

对话伙伴地位创建于2008年。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sectsco.org/EN/show.asp?id=64 |title=Regulations on the Status of Dialogue Partner of the Shanghai Cooperation Organisation |date=28 August 2008 |publisher=The Shanghai Cooperation Organisation |access-date=11 June 2016 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214203708/http://www.sectsco.org/EN/show.asp?id=64 |archive-date=14 February 2012}}</ref>

